com.interpss.dc.pv.module

Interface PVModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PVModelImpl

    public interface PVModel
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'PV Model'. PVModel is contained by the net, and referenced by PVModuleItem. Some of the parameters, such as ShadingFactor could be overrided at individual PVModuleItem level. Data in the model is in Volt and Amp unit

    The following features are supported:

    • Id
    • Name
    • Desc
    • Iv Curve Type
    • Iv Function
    • Iv Curve Points
    See Also:
    PVModulePackage.getPVModel()
